# Maintainer Checks

- [ ] `jsm validate .claude/skills/burpvalve-orchestrator` passes on generated output.
- [ ] `SKILL.md` frontmatter name matches `burpvalve-orchestrator`.
- [ ] Parsed description stays under 500 characters.
- [ ] Every linked reference, example, script, and self-test exists.
- [ ] `.MAINTAINER-CHECKS.md` is not linked from `SKILL.md`.
